data.description: Welcome home to this must-see property located in Palm Harbor’s Village of Woodland Hills. Recently updated kitchen with brand new counter tops, back splash, appliances, and breakfast bar. Laundry and half bath for your guests are on the first floor.  Second floor has primary bedroom with ensuite including dual sinks & walk-in closet, two other bedrooms and full bathroom.   As you walk through the French doors to the over-sized Florida Room, you will see the large fenced in lot overlooking a conservation area located on corner of cul de sac.  Some of the many extras in this home are newer gutters, plantation shutters, washer & dryer, fans, and much more.  This very sought-after, family friendly neighborhood has many amenities including community pool, playground, tennis court, pickleball court, club house, etc.  Located close to airports, hospitals, entertainment, recreation, beaches, restaurants.
